data.description: Is MIDDLETOWN the location you're looking for? Then definitely look at this one, THIS COULD BE THE ONE!!! Close to many amenities (Train station, buses, shopping centers, breweries and many 5-star restaurants). Don't forget it is less than an hour away from the award-winning Museum at Bethel Woods and close to the Casino!  When entering the home, you walk past your 1/2 bathroom with washer and dryer on first floor. Off to your living room with slider to your back patio. Open floor plan from living room to dining area to kitchen which has stainless steel appliances. Walk upstairs to 3 good-sized bedrooms and one full bathroom. NO need to worry about cutting the lawn or paying for garbage removal as the HOA covers it. Close to major highways( NYS route 17 and I84). Schedule your appointment today this won't last.
